%% Diagram: cc::Scheduler pipeline and back-pressure
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant S as cc::Scheduler
    participant MT as Main Thread<br/>(Blink + ProxyMain)
    participant CT as Compositor Thread<br/>(ProxyImpl)

    S->>MT: BeginImplFrame → BeginMainFrame
    activate MT
    Note over MT: rAF, style, layout,<br/>prepaint, paint
    MT->>CT: NotifyReadyToCommit (mutex)

    alt Pending tree already activated
        Note over MT: Blocked briefly<br/>on mutex only
        CT->>CT: ScheduledActionCommit<br/>(push to pending tree)
        CT-->>MT: Release mutex
        deactivate MT
    else Pending tree NOT yet activated
        Note over MT: Back-pressure:<br/>blocked until activation
        CT->>CT: Finish raster
        CT->>CT: Activate (pending → active)
        CT->>CT: ScheduledActionCommit
        CT-->>MT: Release mutex
    end

    Note over CT: ReadyToActivate → Activate<br/>→ ReadyToDraw → Draw
    CT->>S: Frame submitted to Viz
